definitions.definition: A market town and civil parish with a town council in North Northamptonshire district, Northamptonshire , England ( OS grid ref SP8678 ) .
A former borough in Northamptonshire with its headquarters in the town, abolished 1 April 2021 and merged into North Northamptonshire .
A census-designated place in Prince George's County , Maryland , United States .
A city in Montgomery County and Greene County , Ohio , United States .
A former Free Village in Trelawny parish, Jamaica , now part of Duncans .
A coastal town in Kingborough council area, Tasmania , Australia .
